<p>President Trump said on Friday that Venezuela&#x27;s Nicolás Maduro &quot;doesn&#x27;t want to fuck around&quot; with the United States and had offered &quot;everything,&quot; including oil, to ease tensions between Washington and Caracas [reuters.com#1][cbsnews.com#1][theguardian.com#1][ndtv.com#1][theglobeandmail.com#1]. His remarks came as he has acknowledged authorizing CIA covert operations in Venezuela and as the U.S. increases military pressure in the Caribbean [reuters.com#1][ft.com#1][lemonde.fr#1]. Trump made the comments at the White House during a joint appearance with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy [reuters.com#1]. Venezuela&#x27;s government has rejected reports of internal negotiations to remove Maduro, with Vice President Delcy Rodríguez posting a selfie with him and denouncing &quot;liars&quot; [reuters.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/LRZx5lZia8Ph8lU-CtKLu7aQc6Q7K0d3f6S9ACPpdsk-IbXposbK8mAJzwbSy2rkTbANiP9MZ-YuFTzz4iVm_DKRtb22aH6-sMiyDcLhBhPzfMdq0og0XQzjy8G6dLC6HKe9ITAs3zT0lgtB9KncW8RlwDfJftVarlicxLCYvoSGVCDjyAQSAEO-qTFx80KdXkTfdlUoU3MNt5MQhHMGkfPXLpWG1o5rJoqSbzVGUfsCIlWWds_5vKwezNuNNbk88TnKyVpfBV1bDeR3Zw' alt='President Trump speaks at the White House during a meeting with Ukraine&#x27;s President Volodymyr Zelenskyy on October 17, 2025.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Force posture: The U.S. buildup around the Caribbean includes guided missile destroyers, F-35 fighter jets, a nuclear submarine, and roughly 6,500 troops [reuters.com#1].</li><li>Maritime strike: A U.S. strike on a suspected Caribbean drug vessel on Thursday killed two people, and two survivors are being held aboard a U.S. Navy ship [reuters.com#1][theglobeandmail.com#1].</li><li>Campaign framing: Trump has cast the pressure on Caracas as part of a campaign against a &quot;narcoterrorist&quot; threat he links to Maduro [reuters.com#1].</li><li>Potential escalation: Trump has signaled he was considering strikes on land targets in Venezuela, amid broader speculation about regime pressure [lemonde.fr#1].</li></ul><blockquote>He&#x27;s offered everything. You&#x27;re right. You know why? Because he doesn&#x27;t want to fuck around with the United States. - President Donald Trump</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>U.S. President Trump: Says Maduro has offered &quot;everything,&quot; including natural resources, to reduce tensions and avoid conflict. (<a href='https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-venezuelan-president-maduro-doesnt-want-fuck-around-with-us-2025-10-17/'>Reuters</a>)</li><li>Venezuelan government: Dismisses reports of internal negotiations to oust Maduro, with Vice President Delcy Rodríguez posting a selfie with him and denouncing &quot;liars.&quot;. (<a href='https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-venezuelan-president-maduro-doesnt-want-fuck-around-with-us-2025-10-17/'>Reuters</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/article-donald-trump-expletive-venezuela-nicolas-maduro-strikes-drug-vessel/'>Trump uses expletive in remarks about Venezuelan President Maduro</a> - theglobeandmail.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2025/oct/17/trump-maduro-venezuela'>Trump claims Maduro willing to give ‘everything’ to ease US tensions</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ft.com/content/428becc8-240f-4ab5-9ff8-a37bc609e614'>Trump says Nicolás Maduro offered concessions to head off US military pressure</a> - ft.com</li><li><a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/video/trump-says-venezuelas-maduro-offered-oil-to-us-amid-escalating-tensions/'>Trump says Venezuela&#x27;s Maduro offered oil to U.S. amid escalating tensions</a> - cbsnews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/nicolas-maduro-donald-trump-venezuelas-maduro-doesnt-want-to-f-around-with-us-donald-trump-9476616#publisher=newsstand'>Venezuela&#x27;s Maduro Doesn&#x27;t Want To F*** Around With US: Donald Trump</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.reuters.com/